</nav></header><main aria-label="main content"><div class="speakable">
      <b data-is-speakable>6 Ways To Make Creativity Part Of Your Everyday Life: Life Kit</b>   <b data-is-speakable>Professional artists aren't the only people who can make art. In this episode, learn how to weave art into your everyday life. Because whether you're doodling, making pottery or embroidering, creativity is good for you and your health.</b>
</div>
